<p>Hi <%= @person.name.presence || "there" %>,</p>

<p>
  Good news: EUSA has paid <%= @expenses.size == 1 ? "your expense" : "your expenses" %>.
  The money should reach your account shortly, if it hasn't already.
</p>

<ul>
  <% @expenses.each do |expense| %>
    <li>
      <%= expense.description.presence || "Expense ##{expense.auto_number}" %>:
      <%= reimbursements_money(expense.amount || 0) %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Thanks for your patience, and thanks for everything you do for Bedlam Fringe.</p>

<p>The Bedlam Fringe finance team</p>
